                "An HFL process is performed on a network topology made up of various connected devices.\nThe topology of these devices are arranged as a tree (see ",
                "Fig. 2",
                ").\nThe device at the root of this tree—the ",
                "global aggregator",
                " in ",
                "Fig. 2",
